snippet.title: Moonfrost Livestream Founder Update Ep 2
snippet.description:
Welcome to Moonfrost a modern-day life-sim farming RPG set in a beautiful next gen pixel-art world.

Come join us in our Founder Updates Series on Tuesday 2nd July at 15:00 UTC, with Gina our Boss Witch, Co Founder & Art Director and Jase our Marketing & Community Lead! 

You can also head to our channel to find out about our latest news and previous updates!  

Website: https://moonfrost.io/
Twitter:  https://moonfrost.io/
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/moonfrost
